112
00:04:55,840 --> 00:04:59,000
 "a fragrant offering and sacrifice to God.

113
00:04:59,000 --> 00:05:02,500
 "But sexual immorality and all impurity or covetousness

114
00:05:02,500 --> 00:05:04,360
 "must not even be named among you

115
00:05:04,360 --> 00:05:06,360
 "as is proper among saints.

116
00:05:06,360 --> 00:05:08,560
 "Let there be no filthiness, nor foolish talk,

117
00:05:08,560 --> 00:05:11,760
 "nor crude joking, which are all out of place.

118
00:05:11,760 --> 00:05:14,340
 "But instead, let there be thanksgiving,

119
00:05:14,340 --> 00:05:15,540
 "for you may be sure of this,

120
00:05:15,540 --> 00:05:18,940
 "that everyone who is sexually immoral or impure

121
00:05:18,940 --> 00:05:21,480
 "or who is covetous, that is an idolater,

122
00:05:21,480 --> 00:05:24,960
 "has no inheritance in the kingdom of Christ and God.

123
00:05:24,960 --> 00:05:27,160
 "Let no one deceive you with empty words,

124
00:05:27,160 --> 00:05:28,420
 "for because of these things,

125
00:05:28,420 --> 00:05:31,800
 "the wrath of God comes upon the sons of disobedience.

126
00:05:31,800 --> 00:05:33,560
 "Therefore do not become partners with them,

127
00:05:33,560 --> 00:05:35,760
 "for at one time you were darkness,

128
00:05:35,760 --> 00:05:37,660
 "but now you are light in the Lord.

129
00:05:37,660 --> 00:05:39,640
 "Walk as children of light,

130
00:05:39,640 --> 00:05:40,960
 "for the fruit of light is found

131
00:05:40,960 --> 00:05:43,560
 "in all that is good and right and true.

132
00:05:43,560 --> 00:05:46,160
 "And try to discern what is pleasing to the Lord.

133
00:05:46,160 --> 00:05:48,360
 "Take no part in the unfruitful works of darkness,

134
00:05:48,360 --> 00:05:50,080
 "but instead expose them.

135
00:05:50,080 --> 00:05:51,360
 "For it is shameful even to speak

136
00:05:51,360 --> 00:05:53,520
 "of the things that they do in secret.

137
00:05:53,520 --> 00:05:55,340
 "But when anything is exposed by the light,

138
00:05:55,340 --> 00:05:56,840
 "it becomes visible,

139
00:05:56,840 --> 00:05:59,340
 "for anything that becomes visible is light.

140
00:05:59,340 --> 00:06:01,980
 "Therefore it says, awake, O sleeper,

141
00:06:01,980 --> 00:06:05,180
 "and arise from the dead, and Christ will shine on you."

142
