 That, along with filthiness, foolish talk, crude joking,

162
00:07:09,360 --> 00:07:12,320
 that's who I was.

163
00:07:12,320 --> 00:07:13,600
 I know that.

164
00:07:13,600 --> 00:07:14,760
 I have a new identity.

165
00:07:14,760 --> 00:07:18,000
 But what if I feel like that's who I still am?

166
00:07:18,000 --> 00:07:22,820
 You know, I know what I'm supposed to feel.

167
00:07:22,820 --> 00:07:27,820
 I know my identity is as a beloved child of God.

168
00:07:27,820 --> 00:07:31,460
 But what if I'm still feeling or drawn to

169
00:07:31,460 --> 00:07:35,440
